OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen staying dry and clear overnight
OL,8,Fwith some patchy mist and low cloud.
OL,9,FChilly in sheltered glens.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA dry and warm day with some
OL,12,Fsunshine although some high cloud
OL,13,Faround. Cooler onshore breeze along
OL,14,Fthe east coast. Chance of a few
OL,15,Fevening showers.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA cooler
OL,18,Fand cloudier few days with a chance of
OL,19,Fshowers, although Sunday may see fewer
OL,20,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
